replies.body:
I like the mushrooms growing on mushrooms - part of mme fears it goes all [fractal](http://fc02.deviantart.net/fs45/f/2009/109/3/4/Fractal_Tree_by_TaraRoys.gif) and it's mushrooms all the way down. 
That Blitzcrank silhouette is just perfect - almost t-shirt worthy on its own.

I have to say though, the thumbnail looks like something from Katamari Damacy - so weird :D

Originally wanted to make mushroom fortress...but something went wrong. in any case it's sample  to art in style poster URF mode. in the future will not be so sloppy ^^. now I'm working on another art for Teemo.
